    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1170655605">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1170655605" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1170655605" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1170655605">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/125053053/">星霖</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2017-03-28</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">曾国藩天资不高，智商平平，23岁才中秀才，其后屡次会试失败，但最后却能成为一代儒学大家，清朝中兴第一名臣，关键在于他至始至终的＂自我教育＂，其最大过人之处就是终其一生不断地反思与学习，并以日记方式记录，从而得以进步，成就自我。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1163553334">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1163553334" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1163553334" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1163553334">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/122973123/">你给我听好</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2017-03-12</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">诙谐幽默，通俗易懂，全面了解了一个不一样的曾国藩，受益匪浅。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
